title: Hollydays à la Cigale "Mouzaïa" - Converse Avant-Poste
description:
Parisian duo Hollydays are a one-to-watch in the French music landscape. Their sound is characterized by fresh pop combined with sweet electro tones. Watch Hollydays perform Mouzaïa as part of the Converse Avant-Poste series.

Converse Avant-Poste is a long-term celebration of emerging artists & musicians in the region - and features gigs and regular films of the most exciting new talent from the city. 

Track: "Mouzaïa" by Hollydays

Video editing : Vivien Fossez
Shot by : Alexis Rieger & Vivien Fossez
Sound mix : Henri D'armancourt
